typeorm-cli.ts

argv
Default value : yargs(process.argv.slice(2)) .option('microservice', { alias: 'm', type: 'string', describe: 'The name of the microservice', demandOption: true, }) .option('command', { alias: 'c', type: 'string', describe: 'TypeORM CLI command (e.g., generate, run, revert)', demandOption: true, }) .option('args', { alias: 'a', type: 'string', describe: 'Additional arguments for the TypeORM CLI command (optional)', default: '', }) .option('title', { alias: 't', type: 'string', describe: 'Title for migration file. Needed while running generate (optional)', default: '', }) .help().argv
dataSourcePath
Default value : path.join( __dirname, `./apps/${microservice}/src/typeorm.data-source.ts`, )
typeormCommand
Default value : `ts-node -r tsconfig-paths/register ./node_modules/typeorm/cli.js migration:${command} ${title ? './apps/' + microservice + '/src/migrations/' + title : ''} -d ${dataSourcePath} ${args || ''}`
Default value : argv as { microservice: string; command: string; args?: string; title?: string; }
